<div class="article_body homepage_content">
<p style="padding:0; margin:0 0 6px 0;">In case you missed it, here's how the last seven days looked to Mark:</p>
<p style="padding:0; margin:0 0 6px 0;">The week began with our <i>Song of the Week</i>: the spookiest of cowboy classics, "<a href="https://www.steynonline.com/2058/ghost-riders-in-the-sky" target="_blank">Ghost Riders in the Sky</a>".</p>
<p style="padding:0; margin:0 0 6px 0;">~Monday saw Steyn sally forth in all available media - print, audio and video. First up was his view of the British state's increasing hostility to free speech: "Speakers Cornered" was our <a href="https://www.steynonline.com/8516/speakers-cornered" target="_blank">most-read piece of the week</a>. Next, Mark <a href="https://www.steynonline.com/8517/degrees-of-unpresidentiality" target="_blank">guest-hosted America's Number One radio show</a>...</p>



